James Houlder and girlfriend Vicki Hood fell ill at Sonesta Beach Resort in Sharm El Sheikh, Egypt, last summer .
They had booked the trip for the sun and scuba diving in the Red Sea .
But within hours of arriving they became violently ill with sickness and diarrhoea .
Mr Houlder has since developed Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS) which can leave him in crippling pain .